Let's face it, gospel music has changed significantly over the past 20 to 30 years. So, don't get left behind.  This video is sure to take your days of playing basic 1980 &quot;block&quot; chords to playing some of the most contempory 2000-present &quot;licks&quot; used in today's contemporary gospel music.


&quot;7 Days&quot;

There are many different scales and runs, but how do you tie them together into one complete dynamic solo?  You will be guided through a 7 day program that will introduce different scales, modes and licks to use in your solo masterpeice.  This is a must for Intermediate musicians that are looking for that &quot;edge&quot; in playing and creating melody lines, as well as inserting those dynamic licks that seperate you from the rest.

As an added bonus, you will have a complete understanding of how to create a melody line from scratch, as well as how to implement chords to set the tone for your &quot;blazing&quot; solo masterpeice.


